=David Hawkes 霍克思 (1923-2009)=
==Publications==
===PhD Dissertation===
* The Problem of Date and Authorship in Ch'u Tz'u. Oxford University, 1955
===Monographs===
* Ch'u Tz'u: the Songs of the South. Oxford: Clarendon Press, 1959
* A Little Primer of Tu Fu. Oxford: Clarendon Press, 1967
* The story of the stone: a Chinese novel in five volumes. Harmondsworth: Penguin, 1980
* Liu Yi and the Dragon Princess : a thirteenth-century Zaju play by Shang Zhongxian. Hong Kong: Chinese University Press, 2003